<p>Hi <%= @recipient_name %>,</p>

<% if @ai_generated_intro.present? %>
  <% ai_lines = @ai_generated_intro.to_s.split(/(?<=[.!])/).map(&:strip).reject(&:blank?) %>
  <% if ai_lines.length == 3 %>
    <% merged_lines = [ai_lines[0], ai_lines[1..2].join(' ')] %>
    <%= safe_join(merged_lines.map { |line| content_tag(:p, line) }) if merged_lines.any? %>
  <% else %>
    <%= safe_join(ai_lines.map { |line| content_tag(:p, line) }) if ai_lines.any? %>
  <% end %>
<% else %>
  <p>I analyzed recent reviews for <%= @company_name %> and found customers love the <%= @positive_categories.first(2).map(&:downcase).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %>—solid wins to build on.</p>

  <p>However, feedback on <%= @feedback.first(2).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %> needs your attention, potentially impacting repeats.</p>
<% end %>

<p>Check out our free report on trends here: <%= link_to "View Full Report for #{@company_name}", report_url(@company.business&.place_actor_run_id || @company.place_id), target: '_blank' %>.</p>

<p>Tablr converts these into wins—our partners average 22% more revenue by addressing them.</p>

<p>Open to a 15-minute call to dive in?</p>

<p>Best,<br/>
Haider Ali<br/>
Founder, Tablr<br/>
<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
  Don't want to receive these emails? <%= link_to "Unsubscribe", unsubscribe_url(email: @email), style: "color: #666;" %>
</p>
</p>
